Interface PbcsApplication

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PbcsApplicationImpl

    public interface PbcsApplication
    Models a PBCS application such as a Planning or an HFM application.

    jasonwjones

      • refreshCube

        PbcsJobLaunchResult refreshCube(String cubeRefreshName)
        Refreshes the cube with the refresh name. If the refresh name listed in your cube doesn't work, try using 'CubeRefresh'. During testing this seemed to work even when the refresh name was actually different.
        Parameters:
        cubeRefreshName - the CUBE_REFRESH name
        Returns:
        a job launch result

      • updateSubstitutionVariables

        void updateSubstitutionVariables(Collection<SubstitutionVariable> variables)
        Update a set of substitution variables. This does not replace all the variables in the application, it just updates the ones that have been specified in the collection (contrary to what the REST API docs seem to imply)
        Parameters:
        variables - the variables to update
